modules.description: Processes RSS and Atom feeds, removing duplicate entries and handling paginated content. Constructs valid HTML snippets for feed summaries. Accepts feed URLs, parses XML data, and outputs structured results.

Fetches and processes Atom or RSS feeds, extracting structured data such as titles, links, dates, and authors. Operates on sources, feeds, and posts, enabling aggregation and metadata extraction from web content. Generates Atom entries from a list of posts for unified feed output.
